{
  "texts": [
    "Regarding the number of 360° environments, the proportions were as follows: reCon3D (48%), reConD (3%), reForm3D (24%), and reFormD (24%).",
    "First, reCon3D showed the highest LoS and a balanced LoH, but the worst LoD.",
    "On the other hand, reConD had the second lowest LoS, a good LoD, and the worst LoH.",
    "In turn, reForm3D had the second highest LoS, the best LoD, and an elevated LoH.",
    "Finally, reFormD had the worst Los, but a balanced LoD, and the highest LoH.In the light of those results, the highest LoS and a balanced LoD and LoH can be associated with the RP techniques based on 3D modelling (reCon3D and reForm3D)."
  ]
}